Compilation flags:
========================================
Enable : MODEL=HYDRO
Disable: GRAVITY, PARTICLE


Default setup:
========================================
1. Adopt the Lohner's error estimator on pressure as the refinement criteria
   --> Refinement threshold = 0.80
2. Maximum refinement level (MAX_LEVEL) = 3


Create data file:
========================================
Run convert_to_gamer_format.py to convert mhd256li* data into 
format usable by GAMER, output as UM_IC

Run simulation:
========================================
./gamer

Data analysis:
========================================
Examples in test_plots.ipynb

